Flip Rotate90 direction for RG Arc panel orientation.
The Arc's panel needs 90 degrees CW correction, opposite to OGA-style
devices (which need 270 CW). Change the ROTATE==1 shader to rotate CW.
diff -rupN flycast.orig/core/rend/gles/quad.cpp flycast/core/rend/gles/quad.cpp
--- flycast.orig/core/rend/gles/quad.cpp
+++ flycast/core/rend/gles/quad.cpp
@@ -29,7 +29,7 @@ void main()
 {
 	vtx_uv = in_uv;
 #if ROTATE == 1
-	gl_Position = vec4(-in_pos.y, in_pos.x, in_pos.z, 1.0);
+	gl_Position = vec4(in_pos.y, -in_pos.x, in_pos.z, 1.0);
 #else
 	gl_Position = vec4(in_pos, 1.0);
 #endif
